abstract: Energy Dept sells Teapot Dome oil field in Wyoming to New York-based Stranded Oil Resources for $45.2 million.
lead_paragraph: A private company will finally be able to legally drill in the Teapot Dome oil field.
snippet: A private company will finally be able to legally drill in the Teapot Dome oil field.

headline.main: Wyoming: U.S. Government Sells Teapot Dome Field
